Question 1
List categories where the average price of products is higher than ₹10,000
Assumed Table
Products
---------
product_id
product_name
category
price
Solution
SELECT
   category,
   AVG(price) AS avg_price
FROM Products
GROUP BY category
HAVING AVG(price) > 10000;

