Question 2
Find products with the highest margin (Selling Price − Cost Price) in each category

Assumed Table
Products
---------
product_id
product_name
category
cost_price
selling_price

Solution using Window Function
SELECT
   product_name,
   category,
   margin
FROM
(
   SELECT
       product_name,
       category,
       selling_price - cost_price AS margin,
       ROW_NUMBER() OVER
       (
           PARTITION BY category
           ORDER BY selling_price - cost_price DESC
       ) AS rn
   FROM Products
) x
WHERE rn = 1;

