Question 3
Robinhood Trading System
Retrieve the top 3 cities having the highest number of completed trade orders. 

Tables
trades
Column
order_id
user_id
quantity
status
date
price

users
Column
user_id
city
email
signup_date


Solution
SELECT
   u.city,
   COUNT(*) AS total_orders
FROM trades t
INNER JOIN users u
   ON t.user_id = u.user_id
WHERE t.status = 'Completed'
GROUP BY u.city
ORDER BY total_orders DESC
LIMIT 3;

